{"data":[{"name":"83:1","price":"1. அளவில் மோசடி செய்பவர்களுக்குக் கேடுதான்.","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ لِّلۡمُطَفِّفِينَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5849,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"waylun lil'muṭaffifīna ","translations":["Woe","to those who give less","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["waylun","lil'muṭaffifīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,800],[2,800,4755]]}},{"name":"83:2","price":"2. அவர்கள் மனிதர்களிடம் அளந்து வாங்கினால், நிறைய அளந்து கொள்கின்றனர்.","arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ إِذَا ٱكۡتَالُواْ عَلَى ٱلنَّاسِ يَسۡتَوۡفُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5850,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhīna idhā ik'tālū ʿalā al-nāsi yastawfūna ","translations":["Those who","when","they take a measure","from","the people","they take in full","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhīna","idhā","ik'tālū","ʿalā","al-nāsi","yastawfūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1220],[2,1220,1620],[3,1620,2620],[4,2620,3010],[5,3010,4740],[6,4740,7945]]}},{"name":"83:3","price":"3. மற்றவர்களுக்கு அவர்கள் அளந்து கொடுத்தாலும் அல்லது நிறுத்துக் கொடுத்தாலும் குறைத்து (அவர்களை நஷ்டப்படுத்தி) விடுகின்றனர்.","arabic":"وَإِذَا كَالُوهُمۡ أَو وَّزَنُوهُمۡ يُخۡسِرُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5851,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā kālūhum aw wazanūhum yukh'sirūna ","translations":["But when","they give by measure (to) them","or","they weigh (for) them","they give less","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","kālūhum","aw","wazanūhum","yukh'sirūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,910],[2,910,2210],[3,2210,2500],[4,2500,3750],[5,3750,6895]]}},{"name":"83:4","price":"4, 5. மகத்தான ஒரு நாளில், நிச்சயமாக அவர்கள் (உயிர் கொடுத்து) எழுப்பப்படுவார்கள் என்பதை அவர்கள் நம்பவில்லையா?","arabic":"أَلَا يَظُنُّ أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ أَنَّهُم مَّبۡعُوثُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5852,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"alā yaẓunnu ulāika annahum mabʿūthūna ","translations":["Do not","think","those","that they","(will be) resurrected","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["alā","yaẓunnu","ulāika","annahum","mabʿūthūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,690],[2,690,2400],[3,2400,4610],[4,4610,6470],[5,6470,10305]]}},{"name":"83:5","price":"4, 5. மகத்தான ஒரு நாளில், நிச்சயமாக அவர்கள் (உயிர் கொடுத்து) எழுப்பப்படுவார்கள் என்பதை அவர்கள் நம்பவில்லையா?","arabic":"لِيَوۡمٍ عَظِيمٖ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5853,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"liyawmin ʿaẓīmin ","translations":["For a Day","Great","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["liyawmin","ʿaẓīmin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1030],[2,1030,4045]]}},{"name":"83:6","price":"6. அந்நாளில், மனிதர்கள் அனைவருமே உலகத்தாரின் இறைவன் முன் (விசாரணைக்காக) நின்று கொண்டிருப்பார்கள்.","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَقُومُ ٱلنَّاسُ لِرَبِّ ٱلۡعَٰلَمِينَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5854,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"yawma yaqūmu al-nāsu lirabbi al-ʿālamīna ","translations":["(The) Day","will stand","mankind","before (the) Lord","(of) the worlds","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["yawma","yaqūmu","al-nāsu","lirabbi","al-ʿālamīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,620],[2,620,1490],[3,1490,3130],[4,3130,3940],[5,3940,7905]]}},{"name":"83:7","price":"7. நிச்சயமாக பாவிகளின் பதிவேடு (நரகத்தின்) சிறைக்கூடத்தில் இருக்கும்.","arabic":"كَلَّآ إِنَّ كِتَٰبَ ٱلۡفُجَّارِ لَفِي سِجِّينٖ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5855,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā inna kitāba al-fujāri lafī sijjīnin ","translations":["Nay","Indeed","(the) record","(of) the wicked","(is) surely in","Sijjin","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","inna","kitāba","al-fujāri","lafī","sijjīnin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2559],[2,2559,3699],[3,3699,4509],[4,4509,5769],[5,5769,6329],[6,6329,10014]]}},{"name":"83:8","price":"8. (நபியே!) அச்சிறைக்கூடத்தின் பதிவேட்டை நீர் அறிவீரா?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا سِجِّينٞ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5856,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā adrāka mā sijjīnun ","translations":["And what","can make you know","what","(is) Sijjin","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","adrāka","mā","sijjīnun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2320],[2,2320,3380],[3,3380,3720],[4,3720,7575]]}},{"name":"83:9","price":"9. அது ஒரு பதிவுப்புத்தகம் (தண்டிக்கப்பட வேண்டியவர்களின் பெயர்கள் எல்லாம்) அதில் பதியப்பட்டிருக்கும்.","arabic":"كِتَٰبٞ مَّرۡقُومٞ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5857,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"kitābun marqūmun ","translations":["A book","written","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["kitābun","marqūmun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,910],[2,910,5135]]}},{"name":"83:10","price":"10. (இதைப்) பொய்யாக்குபவர்களுக்கு அந்நாளில் கேடுதான்!","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5858,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"waylun yawma-idhin lil'mukadhibīna ","translations":["Woe","that Day","to the deniers","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["waylun","yawma-idhin","lil'mukadhibīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1680],[2,1680,2660],[3,2660,6475]]}},{"name":"83:11","price":"11. அவர்கள் (இதை மட்டுமா பொய்யாக்குகின்றனர்?) கூலி கொடுக்கும் நாளையும் பொய்யாக்குகின்றனர்.","arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ يُكَذِّبُونَ بِيَوۡمِ ٱلدِّينِ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5859,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhīna yukadhibūna biyawmi al-dīni ","translations":["Those who","deny","(the) Day","(of) the Judgment","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhīna","yukadhibūna","biyawmi","al-dīni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1260],[2,1260,2720],[3,2720,3540],[4,3540,6215]]}},{"name":"83:12","price":"12. வரம்புமீறிய பாவியைத் தவிர (மற்றெவரும்) அதைப் பொய்யாக்க மாட்டான்.","arabic":"وَمَا يُكَذِّبُ بِهِۦٓ إِلَّا كُلُّ مُعۡتَدٍ أَثِيمٍ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5860,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā yukadhibu bihi illā kullu muʿ'tadin athīmin ","translations":["And not","can deny","[of] it","except","every","transgressor","sinful","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","yukadhibu","bihi","illā","kullu","muʿ'tadin","athīmin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,700],[2,700,1750],[3,1750,3770],[4,3770,4550],[5,4550,5240],[6,5240,6210],[7,6210,9285]]}},{"name":"83:13","price":"13. அவனுக்கு நம் வசனங்கள் ஓதிக் காண்பிக்கப்பட்டால், இது முன்னுள்ளோரின் கட்டுக்கதைகள் தான் என்று கூறுகிறான்.","arabic":"إِذَا تُتۡلَىٰ عَلَيۡهِ ءَايَٰتُنَا قَالَ أَسَٰطِيرُ ٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5861,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"idhā tut'lā ʿalayhi āyātunā qāla asāṭīru al-awalīna ","translations":["When","are recited","to him","Our Verses","he says","Stories","(of) the former (people)","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["idhā","tut'lā","ʿalayhi","āyātunā","qāla","asāṭīru","al-awalīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,740],[2,740,1550],[3,1550,2400],[4,2400,3830],[5,3830,4550],[6,4550,5740],[7,5740,9605]]}},{"name":"83:14","price":"14. நிச்சயமாக அவ்வாறல்ல. அவர்கள் செய்து கொண்டிருந்த தீய செயல்களே அவர்களின் உள்ளங்கள் மீது (துருவாகப்படிந்து) மூடிக் கொண்டன. (ஆதலால்தான், இவ்வாறு கூறுகின்றனர்.)","arabic":"كَلَّاۖ بَلۡۜ رَانَ عَلَىٰ قُلُوبِهِم مَّا كَانُواْ يَكۡسِبُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5862,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā bal rāna ʿalā qulūbihim mā kānū yaksibūna ","translations":["Nay","But","(the) stain has covered","[over]","their hearts","(for) what","they used to","earn","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","bal","rāna","ʿalā","qulūbihim","mā","kānū","yaksibūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,940],[2,940,1400],[3,1400,2260],[4,2260,2960],[5,2960,4540],[6,4540,5520],[7,5520,6390],[8,6390,9485]]}},{"name":"83:15","price":"15. அவ்வாறல்ல. (விசாரணைக்காகக் கொண்டு வரப்படும்) அந்நாளில் நிச்சயமாக இவர்கள் தங்கள் இறைவனை விட்டும் தடுக்கப்பட்டு விடுவார்கள்.","arabic":"كَلَّآ إِنَّهُمۡ عَن رَّبِّهِمۡ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لَّمَحۡجُوبُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5863,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā innahum ʿan rabbihim yawma-idhin lamaḥjūbūna ","translations":["Nay","Indeed, they","from","their Lord","that Day","surely will be partitioned","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","innahum","ʿan","rabbihim","yawma-idhin","lamaḥjūbūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2490],[2,2490,4080],[3,4080,4320],[4,4320,5570],[5,5570,6730],[6,6730,10635]]}},{"name":"83:16","price":"16. பின்னர், நிச்சயமாக இவர்கள் நரகத்தில் நுழைவார்கள்.","arabic":"ثُمَّ إِنَّهُمۡ لَصَالُواْ ٱلۡجَحِيمِ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5864,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma innahum laṣālū al-jaḥīmi ","translations":["Then","indeed, they","(surely) will burn","(in) the Hellfire","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","innahum","laṣālū","al-jaḥīmi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1500],[2,1500,3430],[3,3430,4280],[4,4280,7255]]}},{"name":"83:17","price":"17. பின்னர், (இவர்களை நோக்கி) ‘‘நீங்கள் பொய்யாக்கிக் கொண்டிருந்தது இதுதான்'' என்று கூறப்படும்.","arabic":"ثُمَّ يُقَالُ هَٰذَا ٱلَّذِي كُنتُم بِهِۦ تُكَذِّبُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5865,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma yuqālu hādhā alladhī kuntum bihi tukadhibūna ","translations":["Then","it will be said","This","(is) what","you used to","[of it]","deny","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","yuqālu","hādhā","alladhī","kuntum","bihi","tukadhibūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1160],[2,1160,2120],[3,2120,2710],[4,2710,3610],[5,3610,5090],[6,5090,6340],[7,6340,6920],[8,6920,10425]]}},{"name":"83:18","price":"18. அவ்வாறல்ல! நிச்சயமாக நன்மை செய்தவர்களின் பதிவேடு ‘‘இல்லிய்யூன்' என்ற (மேலான) இடத்தில் இருக்கும்.","arabic":"كَلَّآ إِنَّ كِتَٰبَ ٱلۡأَبۡرَارِ لَفِي عِلِّيِّينَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5866,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā inna kitāba al-abrāri lafī ʿilliyyīna ","translations":["Nay","Indeed","(the) record","(of) the righteous","(will be) surely in","Illiyin","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","inna","kitāba","al-abrāri","lafī","ʿilliyyīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2320],[2,2320,3620],[3,3620,4420],[4,4420,5770],[5,5770,6380],[6,6380,9705]]}},{"name":"83:19","price":"19. (நபியே!) ‘இல்லிய்யூன்' என்னும் (மேலான) இடத்தில் இருக்கும் பதிவேடு என்னவென்று நீர் அறிவீரா?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا عِلِّيُّونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5867,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā adrāka mā ʿilliyyūna ","translations":["And what","can make you know","what","(is) Illiyun","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","adrāka","mā","ʿilliyyūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2050],[2,2050,3080],[3,3080,3520],[4,3520,7145]]}},{"name":"83:20","price":"20. அது ஒரு பதிவுப் புத்தகம். அதில் (நல்லவர்களின் பெயர்களெல்லாம்) பதியப்பட்டிருக்கும்.","arabic":"كِتَٰبٞ مَّرۡقُومٞ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5868,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"kitābun marqūmun ","translations":["A book","written","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["kitābun","marqūmun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,880],[2,880,4825]]}},{"name":"83:21","price":"21. ‘முகர்ரப்' (இறைநெருக்கத்திற்குரிய) வானவர்கள் அதை(க் காத்து)ப் பார்த்துக்கொண்டு இருக்கின்றனர்.","arabic":"يَشۡهَدُهُ ٱلۡمُقَرَّبُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5869,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"yashhaduhu al-muqarabūna ","translations":["Witness it","those brought near","(21)"],"transliterationArr":["yashhaduhu","al-muqarabūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1030],[2,1030,4615]]}},{"name":"83:22","price":"22. ஆகவே, நிச்சயமாக நல்லவர்கள் (அந்நாளில்) இன்பம் நிறைந்த சொர்க்கத்தில்,","arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلۡأَبۡرَارَ لَفِي نَعِيمٍ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5870,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"inna al-abrāra lafī naʿīmin ","translations":["Indeed","the righteous","(will be) surely in","bliss","(22)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","al-abrāra","lafī","naʿīmin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1530],[2,1530,2830],[3,2830,3410],[4,3410,6265]]}},{"name":"83:23","price":"23. உயர்ந்த கட்டில்கள் மீது (சாய்ந்த வண்ணம் சொர்க்கத்தின் காட்சிகளைப்) பார்த்துக் கொண்டிருப்பார்கள்.","arabic":"عَلَى ٱلۡأَرَآئِكِ يَنظُرُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5871,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿalā al-arāiki yanẓurūna ","translations":["On","thrones","observing","(23)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿalā","al-arāiki","yanẓurūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,640],[2,640,3379],[3,3379,7274]]}},{"name":"83:24","price":"24. அவர்கள் முகங்களில் அவர்களின் சுகவாசத்தின் செழிப்பை (நபியே!) நீர் அறிந்து கொள்வீர்.","arabic":"تَعۡرِفُ فِي وُجُوهِهِمۡ نَضۡرَةَ ٱلنَّعِيمِ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5872,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"taʿrifu fī wujūhihim naḍrata al-naʿīmi ","translations":["You will recognize","in","their faces","(the) radiance","(of) bliss","(24)"],"transliterationArr":["taʿrifu","fī","wujūhihim","naḍrata","al-naʿīmi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,920],[2,920,1330],[3,1330,2680],[4,2680,3480],[5,3480,7065]]}},{"name":"83:25","price":"25. முத்திரையிடப்பட்டிருக்கும் கலப்பற்ற திராட்சை ரசம் அவர்களுக்குப் புகட்டப்படும்.","arabic":"يُسۡقَوۡنَ مِن رَّحِيقٖ مَّخۡتُومٍ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5873,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"yus'qawna min raḥīqin makhtūmin ","translations":["They will be given to drink","of","a pure wine","sealed","(25)"],"transliterationArr":["yus'qawna","min","raḥīqin","makhtūmin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1230],[2,1230,1460],[3,1460,2520],[4,2520,6395]]}},{"name":"83:26","price":"26. அது கஸ்தூரியால் முத்திரையிடப்பட்டிருக்கும். (பானத்தை) ஆசை கொள்ள விரும்புவோர் அதையே ஆசை கொள்ளவும்.","arabic":"خِتَٰمُهُۥ مِسۡكٞۚ وَفِي ذَٰلِكَ فَلۡيَتَنَافَسِ ٱلۡمُتَنَٰفِسُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5874,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"khitāmuhu mis'kun wafī dhālika falyatanāfasi al-mutanāfisūna ","translations":["Its seal","(will be of) musk","And for","that","let aspire","the aspirers","(26)"],"transliterationArr":["khitāmuhu","mis'kun","wafī","dhālika","falyatanāfasi","al-mutanāfisūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1350],[2,1350,2360],[3,2360,2990],[4,2990,3820],[5,3820,5620],[6,5620,9225]]}},{"name":"83:27","price":"27. அதில் ‘தஸ்னீம்' என்ற (வடிகட்டிய) பானமும் கலந்திருக்கும்.","arabic":"وَمِزَاجُهُۥ مِن تَسۡنِيمٍ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5875,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wamizājuhu min tasnīmin ","translations":["And its mixture","(is) of","Tasneem","(27)"],"transliterationArr":["wamizājuhu","min","tasnīmin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1610],[2,1610,2220],[3,2220,5945]]}},{"name":"83:28","price":"28. (தஸ்னீம் என்பது அல்லாஹ்வுக்குச்) சமீபமானவர்கள் அருந்துவதற்கென ஏற்பட்ட ஒரு (சிறப்பான) சுனையின் நீராகும்.","arabic":"عَيۡنٗا يَشۡرَبُ بِهَا ٱلۡمُقَرَّبُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5876,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿaynan yashrabu bihā al-muqarabūna ","translations":["A spring","will drink","from it","those brought near","(28)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿaynan","yashrabu","bihā","al-muqarabūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,680],[2,680,2640],[3,2640,3010],[4,3010,6825]]}},{"name":"83:29","price":"29. நிச்சயமாக குற்றவாளிகளோ (இன்று) நம்பிக்கை கொண்டவர்களைக் கண்டு (ஏளனமாகச்) சிரிக்கின்றனர்.","arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلَّذِينَ أَجۡرَمُواْ كَانُواْ مِنَ ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُواْ يَضۡحَكُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5877,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"inna alladhīna ajramū kānū mina alladhīna āmanū yaḍḥakūna ","translations":["Indeed","those who","committed crimes","used to","at","those who","believed","laugh","(29)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","alladhīna","ajramū","kānū","mina","alladhīna","āmanū","yaḍḥakūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1480],[2,1480,2520],[3,2520,3530],[4,3530,4400],[5,4400,4740],[6,4740,5790],[7,5790,6870],[8,6870,10255]]}},{"name":"83:30","price":"30. அவர்களின் சமீபமாகச் சென்றால், (பரிகாசமாகத் தங்களுக்குள்) ஒருவருக்கொருவர் கண் ஜாடையும் காட்டிக்கொள்கின்றனர்.","arabic":"وَإِذَا مَرُّواْ بِهِمۡ يَتَغَامَزُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5878,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā marrū bihim yataghāmazūna ","translations":["And when","they passed","by them","they winked at one another","(30)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","marrū","bihim","yataghāmazūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1000],[2,1000,1800],[3,1800,2380],[4,2380,5765]]}},{"name":"83:31","price":"31. (அவர்களை விட்டும் விலகித்) தங்கள் குடும்பத்தார்களிடம் சென்று விட்டபோதிலும், இவர்களுடைய விஷயங்களையே (பரிகாசமாகப் பேசி) மகிழ்ச்சியடைகின்றனர்.","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱنقَلَبُوٓاْ إِلَىٰٓ أَهۡلِهِمُ ٱنقَلَبُواْ فَكِهِينَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5879,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā inqalabū ilā ahlihimu inqalabū fakihīna ","translations":["And when","they returned","to","their people","they would return","jesting","(31)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","inqalabū","ilā","ahlihimu","inqalabū","fakihīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,610],[2,610,3700],[3,3700,5660],[4,5660,6650],[5,6650,8320],[6,8320,11335]]}},{"name":"83:32","price":"32. (வழியில்) இவர்களைக் கண்டால் (இவர்களைச் சுட்டிக் காண்பித்து) ‘‘நிச்சயமாக இவர்கள் வழிகெட்டுப் போனார்கள்'' என்றும் கூறுகின்றனர்.","arabic":"وَإِذَا رَأَوۡهُمۡ قَالُوٓاْ إِنَّ هَٰٓؤُلَآءِ لَضَآلُّونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5880,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā ra-awhum qālū inna hāulāi laḍāllūna ","translations":["And when","they saw them","they said","Indeed","these","surely have gone astray","(32)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","ra-awhum","qālū","inna","hāulāi","laḍāllūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,1850],[3,1850,3850],[4,3850,5100],[5,5100,8900],[6,8900,15075]]}},{"name":"83:33","price":"33. (நம்பிக்கையாளர்களைப் பற்றி எதற்காக இவர்கள் இவ்வளவு கவலைப்படுகின்றனர்?) இவர்கள் அவர்கள் மீது பாதுகாப்பாளர்களாக அனுப்பப்படவில்லையே!","arabic":"وَمَآ أُرۡسِلُواْ عَلَيۡهِمۡ حَٰفِظِينَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5881,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā ur'silū ʿalayhim ḥāfiẓīna ","translations":["But not","they had been sent","over them","(as) guardians","(33)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","ur'silū","ʿalayhim","ḥāfiẓīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2440],[2,2440,3380],[3,3380,4410],[4,4410,7615]]}},{"name":"83:34","price":"34. எனினும், (மறுமை நாளாகிய) இன்றைய தினம் நம்பிக்கை கொண்டவர்கள் அந்நிராகரிப்பவர்களைக் கண்டு சிரிக்கின்றனர்.","arabic":"فَٱلۡيَوۡمَ ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُواْ مِنَ ٱلۡكُفَّارِ يَضۡحَكُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5882,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fal-yawma alladhīna āmanū mina al-kufāri yaḍḥakūna ","translations":["So today","those who","believed ","at","the disbelievers","they will laugh","(34)"],"transliterationArr":["fal-yawma","alladhīna","āmanū","mina","al-kufāri","yaḍḥakūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1040],[2,1040,2110],[3,2110,3220],[4,3220,3560],[5,3560,4770],[6,4770,8485]]}},{"name":"83:35","price":"35. (சொர்க்கத்திலுள்ள சிறந்த) இருக்கைகள் மீது (சாய்ந்த வண்ணம்) இருந்து கொண்டு, இந்தப் பாவிகள் படும் வேதனையைப்) பார்த்துக்கொண்டு,","arabic":"عَلَى ٱلۡأَرَآئِكِ يَنظُرُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5883,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿalā al-arāiki yanẓurūna ","translations":["On","the thrones","observing","(35)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿalā","al-arāiki","yanẓurūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,490],[2,490,3290],[3,3290,7695]]}},{"name":"83:36","price":"36. (மறுமையை) நிராகரித்த இவர்களுக்கு, இவர்களுடைய செயலுக்குத்தக்க கூலி கொடுக்கப்பட்டதா? (என்றும் கேட்பார்கள்.)","arabic":"هَلۡ ثُوِّبَ ٱلۡكُفَّارُ مَا كَانُواْ يَفۡعَلُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5884,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"hal thuwwiba al-kufāru mā kānū yafʿalūna ","translations":["Have (not)","been rewarded","